node.text:
Join us on the latest epic adventure and meet #Akrapovic for the #Audi #RS6 Avant! Notice how the low-down rumble, a strong mid-range and a high frequency top end join in symphony to add aural delight to the incomparable driving excitement!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com

node.title: Akrapovič for the Audi RS 6 Avant

node.text:
Join us in a thrilling world of Akrapovič high-performance exhaust systems as we take you on an epic drive with BMW #M8Competition and our Slip-On Line (Titanium) exhaust system with Evolution Link pipe set (Titanium)! Such performance, sound and passion are not to be missed - discover the untameable soul of #BMW #M8 partnered with an #Akrapovic roar!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com
This Slip-On Line (Titanium) with Evolution Link pipe set does not meet emission compliance requirements for street or highway use.

node.title: BMW M8 Competition (F91) with an Akrapovič exhaust system

node.text: We're proud to announce that #Akrapovic won the prestigious Red Dot Award in the section "Red Dot Award: Brands and Communication Design 2020" for the video Tribute to Superbikes. Enjoy it here!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on August 07, 2021 tagging @suzukimotogp. May be an image of motorcycle.

node.text: #MotoGP postcard: Team Suzuki Ecstar’s #Suzuki #GSXRR and #Akrapovic making a powerful statement before the Michelin® Grand Prix of Styria! #StyrianGP

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on August 06, 2021 tagging @wittmannracing, @walkenhorstmotorsport, and @bmwmotorsport.

node.text: Orchestrated by Marco Wittmann, this #BMW #M6 #GT3 with #Akrapovic is about to play a thrilling tune at Zolder in Belgium! #DTM

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on August 03, 2021 tagging @tech3racing. May be an image of motorcycle.

node.text: These kinds of shots always get us in that special #MotoGP mood! Tech3 KTM Factory Racing #StyrianGP

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Akrapovič Exhaust System on August 02, 2021.

node.text:
Just look at those crafted curves and imagine the smooth sound that enhances the car’s engine tones without any drone. Lighter due to the use of #titanium and a different configuration, this #Akrapovic exhaust for the #MercedesAMG #A35 delivers power and torque levels throughout the entire rev range!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on August 01, 2021 tagging @m_letti304, and @ktmfactoryracing. May be an image of motorcycle, dirt bike and outdoors.

node.text: Red Bull KTM Factory Racing’s Manuel Lettenbichler has claimed third consecutive victory at Red Bull Romaniacs, round four of the FIM Hard Enduro World Championship on his #Akrapovic equipped #KTM 300 EXC TPI. Congrats! (Photo: KTM Images / Future7Media)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 30, 2021 tagging @walkenhorstmotorsport, and @bmwmotorsport. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: The ever more exciting 24 Hours of Spa-Francorchamps is upon us! Walkenhorst Motorsport, armed with the #Akrapovic equipped #BMW #M6 #GT3, will be out to claim the team’s second overall victory, having previously won in 2018! #Spa24h

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 30, 2021. May be an image of saddle-stitched leather.

node.text:
[Pre-order] Our latest exhaust system for the #BMW #M3 / #M4 (G80 / G82 / G83) is available for pre-order at your nearest #Akrapovic retailer!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 29, 2021.

node.text:
Hey there, #Akrapovic for #Suzuki #GSXR1000! Can you believe this small exhaust from ultra-lightweight titanium provides 70% weight savings over stock? If you're after Grand Prix vibes with a racing sound of total exhilaration, this one's for you!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com
This Slip-On Line (Titanium) does not meet emission compliance requirements for street or highway use.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 26, 2021.

node.text:
Combining production quality, optimum performance and a racing sound output, #Akrapovic for the #Yamaha #MT09 is a great choice for riders who demand the very best!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 25, 2021 tagging @triumph_road.spirit, and @ffhphotographie. May be an image of motorcycle.

node.text:
Beautifully created by Road Spirit, #SpeedTwin Carbone is 17 kg lighter than #Triumph Speed Twin upon which it was modelled. To make things better, this lightweight beast is #Akrapovic equipped!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 23, 2021 tagging @paulsjonass41, @brianbogers, @gasgas.official, and @standinggasgas. May be an image of dirt bike and motorcycle.

node.text: Apart from the spectacular roars and exciting twists, there is really no telling what's on the horizon at the #MXGP of Czech Republic! Standing Construct GASGAS Factory Racing’s MC 450F #Akrapovic

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Akrapovič Exhaust System on July 22, 2021.

node.text:
With parts cast in the in-house foundry, such as the valve housing and an X-connection element in the muffler, #Akrapovic Evolution Line (Titanium) fits directly onto the #AlfaRomeo Giulia Quadrifoglio’s stock downpipes.  Enjoy power and torque with significantly reduced back pressure and a head-turning sound!
_ _ _ _
Emission notice: http://emission.akrapovic.com
